text: Department of the Treasury Internal Revenue Service
This transmits obsolete IRM 1.15.22, Records Management, Records Control Schedule for Tax Administration - Compliance.
The IRM material has been moved to Document 12990, Records Control Schedules published November 2012. Document 12990 consolidates the material in IRM 1.15.8 through IRM
This IRM text supersedes IRM 1.15.22, Records Control Schedule for Tax Administration - Compliance, published May 5, 2009.
